			<div class="shadow p-4 mb-5 bg-white rounded why-card">
				<h4>Affordability</h4>
				<p>Metered services (also called pay-per-use) is an type of payment structure in which a customer has access to potentially unlimited resources but only pays for what they actually use.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6 order-1 order-md-2">
			<img class="img fluid" src="/images/affordability.svg" width="250" height="250" alt="affordability illustration" >
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row text-center mt-4">
		<div class="col-md-6">
