				<h4>Green Logistics</h4>
				<p>Reducing encitronmental and other negative impacts associated with the movement and distribution of supplies. Green supply chains seek to reduce negative environmental sourcing/distribution systems and managing reverse logistics to eliminate inefficiencies.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6 order-1 order-md-2">
			<img class="img fluid" src="/images/green-logistics.svg" width="300" height="250" alt="green-logistics illustration" >
